2026-02-14 16:36:16.025 DEBUG 13044 --- [http-nio-8080-exec-4] c.f.exam.mapper.QuestionMapper.update    : ==> Parameters: 某电商平台的订单数据库包含以下表：
1. 顾客表(Customers): customer_id(PK), name, email, join_date
2. 产品表(Products): product_id(PK), name, category, price, stock
3. 订单表(Orders): order_id(PK), customer_id(FK), order_date, total_amount
4. 订单明细表(OrderDetails): detail_id(PK), order_id(FK), product_id(FK), quantity, unit_price

请编写SQL查询完成以下任务：
1. 查询2023年每个月的销售总金额
2. 查询购买过'电子产品'类别且总消费金额超过1000元的顾客姓名和总消费金额
3. 查询库存不足10件的产品中，销量前5的产品名称和剩余库存量(String), 5(Integer), null, 1. SELECT 
      EXTRACT(MONTH FROM order_date) AS month,
      SUM(total_amount) AS monthly_sales
   FROM Orders
   WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM order_date) = 2023
   GROUP BY EXTRACT(MONTH FROM order_date)
   ORDER BY month;

2. SELECT c.name, SUM(o.total_amount) AS total_spent
   FROM Customers c
   JOIN Orders o ON c.customer_id = o.customer_id
   JOIN OrderDetails od ON o.order_id = od.order_id
   JOIN Products p ON od.product_id = p.product_id
   WHERE p.category = '电子产品'
   GROUP BY c.customer_id, c.name
   HAVING SUM(o.total_amount) > 1000;

3. SELECT p.name, p.stock
   FROM Products p
   JOIN OrderDetails od ON p.product_id = od.product_id
   WHERE p.stock < 10
   GROUP BY p.product_id, p.name, p.stock
   ORDER BY SUM(od.quantity) DESC
   LIMIT 5;(String), 这道SQL综合题考察了多表连接、聚合函数、分组查询、条件筛选等核心数据库操作技能。第一小题需要使用EXTRACT函数提取月份信息，并按月分组计算销售总额。第二小题是最复杂的，需要四表连接（顾客-订单-订单明细-产品），通过WHERE筛选电子产品类别，再用HAVING筛选消费总额。这里特别注意GROUP BY要包含所有非聚合列。第三小题考察了排序和限制结果数量，需要连接产品和订单明细表，先筛选低库存产品，再按销量排序取前5。这些查询都是电商系统中典型的分析型查询，体现了SQL在实际业务中的重要作用。解题时要注意表间关联关系和合理的查询性能。(String), 20(Integer), 3(Integer), 584(Integer)
