2026-02-14 21:52:45.815 DEBUG 17300 --- [http-nio-8080-exec-2] c.f.exam.mapper.QuestionMapper.insert    : ==> Parameters: 编写一个Java程序，模拟简单的银行账户管理系统。创建BankAccount类，包含属性：accountNumber(账号)、accountName(户名)、balance(余额)。要求实现存款(deposit)和取款(withdraw)方法，取款时需检查余额是否充足。最后编写测试类创建两个账户对象并进行存取款操作。(String), 5(Integer), null, class BankAccount {
    String accountNumber;
    String accountName;
    double balance;

    public BankAccount(String accountNumber, String accountName, double balance) {
        this.accountNumber = accountNumber;
        this.accountName = accountName;
        this.balance = balance;
    }

    public void deposit(double amount) {
        balance += amount;
    }

    public boolean withdraw(double amount) {
        if (amount > balance) {
            return false;
        }
        balance -= amount;
        return true;
    }
}

public class BankTest {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        BankAccount acc1 = new BankAccount("123456", "张三", 1000);
        BankAccount acc2 = new BankAccount("654321", "李四", 2000);

        acc1.deposit(500);
        boolean success = acc2.withdraw(800);
        System.out.println("取款操作：" + (success ? "成功" : "失败"));
    }
}(String), 本题综合考察面向对象编程能力。BankAccount类封装了银行账户的基本属性和行为，体现了面向对象的封装特性。存款方法直接增加余额，取款方法先进行余额检查，体现了业务逻辑的完整性。测试类中创建多个账户对象进行交互，展示了对象的实例化和方法调用。取款方法返回布尔值作为操作结果，这种设计在实际开发中很常见，可以方便调用者判断操作是否成功。整体上考察了类设计、对象创建、方法定义和基本业务逻辑实现能力。(String), 33(Integer), 3(Integer), Java程序设计(String)
